Package pages

Class LoginPage

java.lang.Object
pages.BasePage
pages.LoginPage
Direct Known Subclasses:
LoginMethods
public class LoginPage extends BasePage
This class represents a login page in a web application, providing methods for interacting with elements on the page. It extends the BasePage class, which provides common methods for interacting with elements on a web page.
